I've bought food for my 2 cats here.  A small place with nice people.  They have nice people there, and they'll take the big bag or package of cans of food out to your car.  They have good selection on better pet food (grain-free Innova Evo, etc.), dry and canned.  I also bought a powdered vitamin supplement for animals.  I'm giving them 4 stars because they don't have any of the frozen raw foods.  Because of that, I'm going to Sunflower Pet Supply now, which is closer to my house (Tempe Feed & Tack was close to my workplace).  Not sure about cat litter, but I don't remember seeing cat or dog carriers.  Don't quote me on that one - just call first.

